  "texts": [
    "In conclusion, while some studies suggest that LTPA in early pregnancy may protect against pre-eclampsia, particularly at moderate intensities, the evidence is not consistent across all studies.",
    "Further research is needed to clarify the relationship between LTPA and pre-eclampsia risk, taking into account the intensity and duration of physical activity, as well as individual differences in susceptibility to the condition.",
    "Additionally, the potential influence of other factors such as prepregnancy BMI and socioeconomic status should be considered (PUBMED:32093248).",
